1
00:00:01,002 --> 00:00:03,035
 hear.                          

2
00:00:03,070 --> 00:00:04,436
          There's another thing:

3
00:00:04,472 --> 00:00:07,773
    Edith inherits Gregson's    
      publishing company.       

4
00:00:07,808 --> 00:00:09,208
           CLARKSON:            
       <i> There is no drug,</i>       

5
00:00:09,243 --> 00:00:12,277
       no electric shock        
that will achieve what you want.

6
00:00:13,848 --> 00:00:15,481
 If the clerk in York remembers 

7
00:00:15,516 --> 00:00:17,516
   selling me a return ticket   
          to London...          

8
00:00:19,186 --> 00:00:21,286
...I'm a dead man.              

